shifts.title: Daily Gate Lead
shifts.description: This is a 12 hours 'on call' shift for those katz who already have enough gate experience to herd our crew and support them in their duties. To apply please contact gate@goingnowhere.org

shifts.title: Gate Crew
shifts.description: This shifts needs at least one person speaking Spanish and at least one person with previous gate experience. You will check tickets and EARLY ENTRY CODES and help people in.

shifts.title: Katz fluffer
shifts.description: You will look after the wellbeing of our gate crew, acting as a link with central services when needed (support the Daily Gate Lead and make sure the katz have their milk and biscuits and take their breaks)
